{"tid":497334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"16歲學生為千元報酬販毒　海關檢獲市值200萬可卡因毒品","createTime":"2017-12-12T15:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T01:42:06.000Z","uid":115415,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"f65e0c3f533425fef20a50f7444a331b030bd529","tid":497334,"uid":115415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:45:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/140893\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F140893&d=Apn2QX6SagC2JEHu3v7nu9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=89e36f61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/140893</a><br />\n<br />\n晚上8時許，海關毒品調查科人員進行反毒品行動，於沙田禾輋邨附近截停一名可疑青少年，於其手挽紙袋中檢獲兩公斤懷疑可卡因毒品，市值約200萬港元。被捕青少年16歲，報稱職業先修學院學生，報稱為1,000多港元的報酬而販毒。海關初步調查該批毒品會在沙田區收交。海關毒品調查科高級督察方向榮指，案件仍在調查中，不過根據以往個案，臨近聖誕節及新年，不少網站會招攬青少年販毒，以賺取快錢，海關呼籲青少年不要為搵快錢以身犯險，販毒是最高刑罰，罰款500萬及終身監禁。"},{"pid":"757ea67c28bab47f036b0d37bd3e75d746d53753","tid":497334,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:45:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/495108/page/12\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/495108/page/12</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a75f19c5b8d3bc6e7e1dcc83179a94f155e77a","tid":497334,"uid":86943,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:45:57.000Z","msg":"做乜呢牌咁多戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468158cab68221b7c164328890b83edf056e3fbc","tid":497334,"uid":45185,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:46:04.000Z","msg":"16歲判廿碌出返嚟都36<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a48adbeee1d5f694b2c8646155780b0c0839232","tid":497334,"uid":49456,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12